Program 'aMemory' is a well-known game for training your HUMAN memory.
The rest of the documentation is provided in doc.E (English), doc.D
(Deutsch), and doc.N (Nederlands).

If you feel like an artist capable of drawing pictures for the amemory
cards, please send them to me for re-distribution.

All the current material is ©opyright by Tis Veugen.  The program is
shareware.  If you like the program, then do not hesitate to send a
donation of $5 (or DM 10 or Fl 10) to me.

